entries.journal_entry_description: Bantha Moving and Storage, on Tatooine, is rumored to be an undercover spice house. Radeld wants the product plans and spice samples from the fake moving company.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Retrieve spice samples from Bantha Moving and Storage. Rumor has it they're using some old buildings in the Tusken outpost to keep their activities secret.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Retrieve the product plans from Bantha Moving and Storage. Rumor has it they're using some old buildings in the Tusken outpost to keep their activities secret.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good job collecting those plans and samples. Come on back and we can settle up.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: With the plans and samples in hand, return to Radeld in Mos Eisley and tell him of a job well done.
